<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1887] Update hbase trunk to latests on hadoop 0.21 branch so we can all test sync/append</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1887</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Update hbase to include hdfs, common, and mr jars... and all their test counterparts.  try to figure what to do about native code.  get it all in so we can start testing sync/append before 0.21 freezes.  See Clint&apos;s hbase-1877.  Something for sure has changed in hdfs.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
